import React, { Component } from 'react'; class About extends Component { render() { return (

About Me

Hey there,

I'm Adriana Soler

Full Stack Web Developer | Marketer | Graphic Designer



• Advertising/Marketing expert with +13 years developing results-oriented promotions, information-driven communications, branding and general advertisements. Highly-skilled creator of awareness-generating marketing programs to business-oriented objectives.

• Professional in managing teams from concept to execution of strategic interactive and print design and marketing projects. • Experience leading a variety of creative projects from websites, animated banner ads and interactive presentations to logos, letterheads, print advertisements, tradeshow graphics, brochures and illustrations.

• Excellent personal and communication skills.

• Able to uncover and capitalize upon unique selling points of diverse products/services.

• Track record of highly successful marketing and advertising.

• Pleasant, enthusiastic, loyal and hardworking with a concern for creativity, quality and high-profitability on all projects.

Specialties: • Able to uncover and capitalize upon unique selling points of diverse products/services. Advertising and marketing.
